### 1) Get cart
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cart

### 2) Add item
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 101,
  "name": "Ruby Ring",
  "unitPrice": 5000,
  "quantity": 2
}

### 3) Update quantity
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/cart/items/101
Content-Type: application/json

{ "quantity": 3 }

### 4) Remove item by itemKey (e.g., product 1, no attribute)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/cart/item/1:0

### OR Remove item by itemKey (e.g., product 2, attribute 5)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/cart/item/2:5

### 5) Checkout
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cart/checkout
